text: Hey @FedEx why have I received 15 calls from an automated call centre telling me I have a package waiting. Which I do not. I’ve called your office 3 times to explain you have the wrong number. Figure it out!  #fail
@Jake0458 Hello Jake, this is Rochelle. You have been receiving a fraudulent call from someone impersonating FedEx.
@FedExHelp Not true. I called FEDEX. They said my number was associated with the tracking number the call gave.
@FedExHelp I dm’d you the whole story. You haven’t responded

@Jake0458 Hello Jake, my name is Rebecca. I apologize for the inconvenience you have experienced and would like to look into this for you.  In order for me to respond, I will need for you to like our page and DM the tracking number and phone number.
Thank you.
